She sat back at her console.  She was missing Scorponok.  She pulled 
out a 3 inch, 3-D hologram of him.  She smiled at it.  It wasn't as 
good as the real thing, but untill he returned, it would have to do.

She turned and looked at Quickstrike standing at the entrance wasy to 
the cave.  She put the hologram away and walked over.  
"Hey commander, I got a message from KitKat a little while back.  she 
said that she would return in a few hours.  I checked her position.  
She near those northern markers of yours."
